duck: Disability Studies Quarterly, the magazine of the Society for Disability Studies

wiki.text:
'DSQ' is an initialism used to abbreviate:
* [[Disability Studies Quarterly]], the magazine of the Society for
  Disability Studies

It is also:
* the file extension for Corel QUERY files
* the language code for Dawsahak, a language of Mali
* DSQ software, founded in 1992 in India
* an abbreviation for "Disqualified" in the Racing Rules of Sailing
wiki.title: DSQ
